&lt;li>Lên website Open Development Vietnam tìm dữ liệu tên là “&lt;em>Reservoirs of the Greater Mekong Subregion; Thailand, Cambodia, Laos, Vietnam and Myanmar&lt;/em>”.&lt;/li>
